				<name type="primary" sortindex="1" value="魔幻特攻 (Magic Special Attack)" />
			
						                           
						               													<description>&amp;#233;&amp;#173;&amp;#148;&amp;#229;&amp;#185;&amp;#187;&amp;#231;&amp;#137;&amp;#185;&amp;#230;&amp;#148;&amp;#187;, roughly translated as &amp;quot;Magic Special Attack&amp;quot;, is a two player game where the players compete to score the most points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The players are illusionists erecting barriers in an arena of limited space.  When a player erects a barrier, they earn a gem of that color.  In lieu of placing a normal barrier on their turn, a player may also pay a gem to place a special barrier of the corresponding color.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If through either type a barrier placement a player creates a 1x1 isolated space, they may earn a bonus gem.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;One round ends when one of the players cannot place an additional barrier. The game lasts over four rounds and points are awarded for earning a certain number of gems of each color and for sets of gems.  The player with the most points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game was originally released as part of the 2021 150BG.con convention in Taiwan, where games sell for 150 TWD, roughly $5 USD.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
